Name: Call notes
Description: The body of the call

Name: Call direction
Description: The direction of a call

Name: Call outcome
Description: The outcome of the call

Name: Call duration
Description: The duration of the call, in milliseconds

Name: From number
Description: The phone number of the person that initiated the call

Name: From Number Name
Description: The name of the phone number that initiated the call

Name: Transcript Available
Description: Flag to indicate if the call has an associated transcript

Name: Voicemail Available
Description: Flag to indicate if the call has an associated voicemail

Name: Recording URL
Description: The URL of the recorded call audio

Name: Call Source
Description: The source of the call to differentiate VoIP vs Video Conferencing Apps
Options: VoIP (VOIP) [READ-ONLY]; Zoom (ZOOM) [READ-ONLY]; Integrations Platform (INTEGRATIONS_PLATFORM) [READ-ONLY]; HubSpot Meetings (HUBSPOT_MEETINGS) [READ-ONLY]; In Person Meetings (IN_PERSON_MEETINGS) [READ-ONLY]

Name: Call status
Description: The status of the call
Options: Busy (BUSY); Calling CRM User (CALLING_CRM_USER); Canceled (CANCELED); Completed (COMPLETED); Connecting (CONNECTING); Failed (FAILED); In Progress (IN_PROGRESS); Missed (MISSED); No Answer (NO_ANSWER); Queued (QUEUED); Ringing (RINGING); On Hold (HOLD)

Name: Call summary
Description: A generated summary of the call

Name: Call Title
Description: The title of the call

Name: To Number
Description: The phone number of the person that was called

Name: To Number Name
Description: The name of the phone number that was called

Name: Tracked terms
Description: A list of any tracked terms contained in the call transcript

Name: Connected count
Description: This counter is used to report on the total number of calls that end up connected to a live recipient

Name: Voicemail count
Description: This counter is used to report on the total number of calls that end up with a voicemail

Name: Created by user ID
Description: The user who created this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Merged record IDs
Description: The list of record IDs that have been merged into this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Record ID
Description: The unique ID for this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Record source detail 1
Description: First level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source detail 2
Description: Second level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source detail 3
Description: Third level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source
Description: How this record was created.

Name: Updated by user ID
Description: The user who last updated this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Call and meeting type
Description: The activity type of the engagement

Name: Attached file IDs
Description: The IDs of the files that are attached to the engagement

Name: Activity created by
Description: The user who created the engagement

Name: Create date
Description: The date that an engagement was created

Name: Last modified date
Description: The date any property on this engagement was modified

Name: Activity date
Description: The date that an engagement occurred

Name: Activity assigned to
Description: The user that the activity is assigned to in HubSpot. This can be any HubSpot user or Salesforce integration user, and can be set manually or via Workflows.

Name: HubSpot Team
Description: The team of the owner of an engagement.
